ion function of any number $n$\nof fermion stress tensors $\\langle TT\\dots T\\rangle$ may be expressed as a\ncombinatoric sum of $n!/2$ linear tree diagrams of the scalar boson.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 18:51:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Dec 2014 18:51:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-09"}
