 of our work is the novel use of coding-theoretic tools like\ndensity evolution methods for the design and analysis of fast and efficient\nalgorithms for compressive phase-retrieval problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 21:40:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2017 00:36:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-03"}
